  "monster": {
    "title": "Roryxt.",
    "body": "One of the many lords of Pandemonium, Roryxt has an armoured light green body with large, powerful wings and a skull for a head. It looks diseased.\n\n<lightgrey>Max HP: 182     </lightgrey><lightgrey> Will: +++      </lightgrey><lightgrey>   AC: ++++ +   </lightgrey><lightgrey>  EV: ++        </lightgrey>                \n<darkgrey>    rF: ...     </darkgrey><lightgrey>   rC: +..      </lightgrey><lightgrey>rPois: +        </lightgrey><lightgrey>rNeg: ∞         </lightgrey><lightgrey>rElec: +        </lightgrey>\n<lightgrey>Threat: Lethal  </lightgrey><lightgrey>Class: Demonic  </lightgrey><lightgrey> Size: Large    </lightgrey><lightgrey> Int: Human     </lightgrey>\nSpeed: 170% (normally travels faster than you)\n\nYou have about 86% to hit with the +8 autumn katana and 82% to hit with your bite.\nIt has about 46% to hit you.\n\nAttack  Max Damage  \nHit     37          \n\nIt is immune to torment; and resistant to miasma.\nIt can see invisible.\nIt can fly.\nIt can open doors.\nSPELLSET_PLACEHOLDERTo read a description, press the key listed above. (AdB) indicates damage (the sum of A B-sided dice), (x%) indicates the chance to defeat your Will, and (y) indicates the spell range; shown in red if you are in range.\n\nIt is currently targeting the dire elephant.\n\nThis monster has been temporarily summoned to this location. If angered it will immediately vanish, yielding no experience or items; it is incapable of using stairs.",
